item.title: Polls: Trump, Clinton lead big in NY, PA
item.description: Donald Trump is leading his rivals for the Republican nomination by more than 20 points in the upcoming primary contests of New York and Pennsylvania, according to a pair of Fox News polls released Sunday.

item.title: How Colo. confusion could spell trouble

item.title: Official: Terrorists planned to strike again
